<div class="page-head">
  <div>
    <h1>Reports</h1>
    <p>Board-ready quarterly report — pulse, top risks, incidents, exercises, compliance, vendors.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="actions">
    <a class="btn" href="/reports/board">Preview this quarter</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
  <div class="kpi">
    <div class="k-label">Program pulse (live)</div>
    <div class="k-value"><%= metrics.pulse %>/100</div>
    <div class="k-delta"><%= metrics.pulse >= 80 ? 'Strong' : metrics.pulse >= 65 ? 'Healthy' : metrics.pulse >= 50 ? 'Caution' : 'At risk' %></div>
  </div>
  <div class="kpi">
    <div class="k-label">Open risks</div>
    <div class="k-value"><%= metrics.counts.openRisks %>/<%= metrics.counts.totalRisks %></div>
    <div class="k-delta">Top risk: <%= (metrics.topRisks[0] && metrics.topRisks[0].title) || '—' %></div>
  </div>
  <div class="kpi">
    <div class="k-label">Incidents · Exercises</div>
    <div class="k-value"><%= metrics.counts.incidentCount %> · <%= metrics.counts.exerciseCount %></div>
    <div class="k-delta">Last 90 days</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-head"><div class="card-title">Generate Board Report (Word)</div></div>
    <p class="muted" style="font-size:13px; margin-bottom:12px;">
      Produces a branded executive report for <%= metrics.label %>. Includes pulse analysis, top 10 risks, incidents by severity, exercise outcomes, compliance maturity, and vendor concentration. An AI-written executive narrative is included by default.
    </p>
    <form method="POST" action="/reports/board.docx" data-ai="Composing the board narrative and assembling metrics…">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        <label style="font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-secondary);">
          Period start
          <input type="date" name="start" value="<%= metrics.periodStart %>" style="width:100%;">
        </label>
        <label style="font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-secondary);">
          Period end
          <input type="date" name="end" value="<%= metrics.periodEnd %>" style="width:100%;">
        </label>
      </div>
      <label style="font-size:12.5px; color:var(--text-secondary);">
        Period label (shown on cover)
        <input type="text" name="label" value="<%= metrics.label %>" style="width:100%; margin-bottom:12px;">
      </label>
      <label style="display:flex; gap:6px; align-items:center; cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:12px;">
        <input type="checkbox" name="skip_narrative"> Skip AI narrative (use metrics only)
      </label>
      <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Export .docx</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-head"><div class="card-title">What's in the report</div></div>
    <ol style="padding-left:18px; font-size:13.5px; line-height:1.8;">
      <li><strong>Cover + pulse score</strong> — composite of risk, exercise, and compliance health</li>
      <li><strong>Executive narrative</strong> — AI-written 4-section board brief (optional)</li>
      <li><strong>Top 10 risks</strong> — ranked by score, with owner and status</li>
      <li><strong>Incidents this period</strong> — by severity, with details table</li>
      <li><strong>Exercise outcomes</strong> — tabletops, walkthroughs, simulations</li>
      <li><strong>Compliance maturity</strong> — per framework, with implementation %</li>
      <li><strong>Coverage of critical processes</strong> — which BIA processes have a plan, which are exposed</li>
      <li><strong>Vendor concentration</strong> — top 5 critical suppliers</li>
      <li><strong>Sign-off page</strong></li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>
